description:
Carnival Eats - Season 2, Episode 4




From Small Town to Farmville

On this episode, host Noah Cappe travels to the Nederland Heritage Festival, where food from around the world is prepared by an army of volunteers. Later, he travels to Farmville, NC for the Dogwood Festival - home to southern comfort food with a fair flare.




Original Air Date: 06-Aug-2015
